    "40515114": {
      "title": "Faster Exact Bandwidth",
      "abstract": "We deal with exact algorithms for Bandwidth , a long studied NP-hard problem. For a long time nothing better than the trivial O *(n !) exhaustive search was known. In 2000, Feige an Kilian [4] came up with a O *(10 n )-time algorithm. Since then there has been a growing interest in exponential time algorithms but this bound has not been improved. ::: ::: In this paper we present a new and quite simple O *(5 n ) algorithm. We also obtain even better bound in some special cases."
    }
